Class CompanyAgentMessageScheme

    DefaultCompanyAgentMessageScheme, UniformMessageScheme

    public abstract class CompanyAgentMessageScheme
extends MessageScheme
    Class representing an abstraction of message schemes originating from company agents. This class is (currently) used only to structure the respective MessageSchemes and doesn't offer any additional functionality.
